N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5012.3 - Effect of establishment of accounts

State Regulations

The establishment of such accounts shall not be considered to
afford such person or persons any rights of membership in this system nor to
confer upon them any other right except the right to claim such funds under
this Chapter. Notes
